<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="get-away-from">get away from</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>离开；外出度假；摆脱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I won't be able to get away from the office before 7.
7点前我不能离开办公室。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had hoped to take a holiday this year but I wasn't able to get away.
我本想今年去度假，但没能如愿。</p><footer>2013天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I needed to get away from the pressures of work.
我需要排遣工作的压力。</p></div></div>